---

<div id="features" class="px-6 py-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #191919; border-left: 1px solid #191919; border-right: 1px solid #191919;">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Powerful Features for Local Debugging</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed">Everything you need to debug faster and ship with confidence</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Real-time Error Tracking -->
    <div class="text-left p-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Real-time Error Tracking</h3>
      <p class="text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Catch errors as they happen with instant notifications in your browser. No need to check logs or refresh pages.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-[#a5a5a5] text-sm space-y-1">
        <li>• Stack traces with source maps</li>
        <li>• Browser and device context</li>
        <li>• User actions breadcrumbs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Tracing -->
    <div class="text-left p-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 3a1 1 0 000 2v8a2 2 0 002 2h2.586l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 15.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L12.414 15H15a2 2 0 002-2V5a1 1 0 100-2H3zm11.707 4.707a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 9.586 8.707 8.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Performance Tracing</h3>
      <p class="text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Visualize the complete flow of your application with distributed tracing across frontend and backend.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-[#a5a5a5] text-sm space-y-1">
        <li>• Database query timing</li>
        <li>• API request waterfall</li>
        <li>• Component render times</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Unified Console & Logs -->
    <div class="text-left p-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h4a1 1 0 010 2H6.414l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L5 6.414V8a1 1 0 01-2 0V4zm9 1a1 1 0 110-2h4a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 11-2 0V6.414l-2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L13.586 5H12zm-9 7a1 1 0 112 0v1.586l2.293-2.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L6.414 15H8a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4zm13-1a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1h-4a1 1 0 110-2h1.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 111.414-1.414L15 13.586V12a1 1 0 011-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">Unified Console & Logs</h3>
      <p class="text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Capture console logs, warnings, and errors alongside your application events for complete debugging context.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-[#a5a5a5] text-sm space-y-1">
        <li>• Console.log integration</li>
        <li>• Network request logs</li>
        <li>• Custom debug messages</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- AI-Assisted Debugging -->
    <div class="text-left p-6">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
          <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-white">AI-Assisted Debugging</h3>
      <p class="text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Connect Spotlight to your AI coding assistant through MCP for intelligent error analysis and fix suggestions.
      </p>
      <ul class="text-[#a5a5a5] text-sm space-y-1">
        <li>• MCP server integration</li>
        <li>• Cursor IDE support</li>
        <li>• Automated root cause analysis</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-16">
    <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to debug like a pro?</h3>
    <p class="text-xl text-[#a5a5a5] leading-relaxed mb-8">Join developers using Spotlight to fix bugs faster</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <a
        href="/docs/about/"
        class="px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors text-white no-underline"
      >
        Learn More
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/getsentry/spotlight"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer noopener"
        class="px-8 py-3 border border-slate-600 hover:border-slate-500 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors text-white no-underline"
      >
        View on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>